Ignore Python cache files

pycache/
*.pyc

Ignore user uploaded images/documents (so we don't overwrite live files)

static/uploads/profiles/*
static/uploads/documents/*

Keep the folders themselves, just ignore the files inside

!static/uploads/profiles/.gitkeep
!static/uploads/documents/.gitkeep